<h2 id="who-we-are-and-what-we-do">Who we are and what we do</h2>

<h3 id="our-work">Our work</h3>

<p>The information we publish is set into classes. These classes are:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about">what we do</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=transparency-data&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">transparency</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">announcements</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=speech&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">speeches</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="roles-and-responsibilities">Roles and responsibilities</h3>

<p>Information about roles and responsibilities at <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions#ministers">ministers</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions#management">management</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="policy-development">Policy development</h3>

<p>You can find out about our policies at:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/policies?keywords=&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">policies</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=policy-papers&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">policy publications</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="legislation">Legislation</h3>

<p>Information about the legislation that impacts on <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> policies is available at <a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/">legislation.gov.uk</a>.</p>

<h3 id="organisations-the-department-is-responsible-for-sponsors-or-works-in-partnership-with">Organisations the department is responsible for, sponsors or works in partnership with</h3>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations#department-for-work-pensions">Organisations <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> works with</a> include a number of agencies and public bodies.</p>

<h3 id="contacting-the-department">Contacting the department</h3>

<p>Visit <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions#org-contacts">contact us</a> for all <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> contact details.</p>

<h2 id="what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it">What we spend and how we spend it</h2>

<p>Information about what we spend includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>audit reports</li>
  <li>pay and grading structures</li>
  <li>hospitality and expenses</li>
  <li>payments to suppliers</li>
  <li>information about contracts</li>
</ul>

<p>We publish this information in:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=corporate-reports&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">corporate reports</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=transparency-data&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">transparency publications</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/procurement/">procurement procedures</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="our-priorities">Our priorities</h2>

<p>Read about <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about#priorities">our priorities</a> to find out what we’re focusing on and how we’re doing.</p>

