<h2 id="guides-available-on-request">Guides available on request</h2>
<p>Some <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> publications are not available on the website. But you can ask the owner of the guide for a copy.</p>

<h3 id="jobseekers-allowance-jsa-procedural-guidance">Jobseeker’s Allowance (<abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr>) procedural guidance</h3>

<p>This guidance is for <abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr> processors and other <abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr> staff. It provides end-to-end guidance on processing <abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr> claims. This guide is a large document consisting of a number of chapters. When requesting a copy of this, please tell us which chapters you are interested in.</p>

