<h3 id="labour-market-conditions-guide">Labour market conditions guide</h3>

<p>This guidance is for <abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr> staff and labour market decision makers on the labour market conditions for <abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr> and how to refer these. This guide is a large document consisting of a number of chapters. When requesting a copy of this, please tell us which chapters you are interested in.</p>

